(618, 259, 'wp_travel_engine_setting', 'a:11:{s:15:\"trip_prev_price\";s:5:\"18999\";s:4:\"sale\";s:1:\"1\";s:10:\"trip_price\";s:5:\"14555\";s:13:\"trip_duration\";s:1:\"7\";s:20:\"trip_duration_nights\";s:1:\"6\";s:10:\"trip_facts\";a:4:{s:8:\"field_id\";a:2:{i:1;s:14:\"transportation\";i:3;s:8:\"altitude\";}s:10:\"field_type\";a:2:{i:1;s:4:\"text\";i:3;s:4:\"text\";}i:1;a:1:{i:1;s:11:\"1-12 people\";}i:3;a:1:{i:3;s:8:\"Moderate\";}}s:11:\"tab_content\";a:2:{s:10:\"1_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"map_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";}s:9:\"itinerary\";a:3:{s:15:\"itinerary_title\";a:7:{i:1;s:33:\"Delhi –Shimla (370 kms/8-9 hrs)\";i:2;s:24:\"Shimla-Kufri-Sightseeing\";i:3;s:41:\"MANALI –KULLU-SHIMLA (270KMS / 7-8 HRS)\";i:4;s:19:\"Manali- Sightseeing\";i:5;s:35:\"MANALI-Rohtang Pass up to snow line\";i:6;s:40:\"Manali – CHANDIGARH (275 KMS/ 8-9 HRS)\";i:7;s:37:\"CHANDIGARH- DELHI (280 KMS / 5-6 HRS)\";}s:17:\"itinerary_content\";a:7:{i:1;s:174:\"MEALS: Dinner only\r\nOn arrival Delhi Airport you will meet with our assisted and drive for Shimla, on arrival check in to the hotel, Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel…\";i:2;s:304:\"MEALS: Breakfast &amp; Dinner only\r\nToday morning after breakfast proceed towards famous ski Point - KUFRI (Including Kufri Fun Park).  Rest of the evening free to explore THE MALL ROAD, RIDGE, SCANDAL POINT, LAKKAR BAZAAR, CHRIST CHURCH AND LOWER BAZAAR BY OWN. Dinner &amp; Overnight stay at the hotel.\";i:3;s:306:\"MEALS:  Breakfast &amp; Dinner\r\nAfter breakfast check out from the hotel and drive to Shimla enrooted visit Kullu, valley, Kullu shawl industry, Vaishno Devi Temple. Have photographs at Pandoh Dam &amp; Sundernaggar Lake. Evening reach Shimla and check into the hotel. Dinner &amp; overnight stay at hotel.\";i:4;s:490:\"MEALS:   Breakfast &amp; Dinner only\r\nToday morning after breakfast  proceed to half day city tour of Manali which includes- HADIMBA DEVI TEMPLE (Built in 1553 A.D , is Dedicated to Himachal\'s Most Significant Deity Hadimba Mata) VASHISTH HOT SPRINGS (Dedicated to Vashisth Muni &amp; Renowned for its hot Curable water),CLUB HOUSE. Later free to explore the local market (MALL ROAD &amp; IBEX MARKET) of Manali, TIBETAN MONASTERY AND VAN VIHAR by own. Dinner &amp; overnight stay at hotel.\";i:5;s:377:\"MEALS: Breakfast &amp; Dinner only\r\nToday have excursion trip to ROHTANG PASS up to snow line (up to Snow line refers to the barrier placed by the government to avoid risks during Heavy snowfall).  Tour to Rohtang covers some of the most attractive spots, panorama activities and spectacular sight of glaciers. IN EVENING RETURN TO MANALI. Dinner &amp; overnight stay at hotel.\";i:6;s:181:\"MEALS:  Breakfast &amp; Dinner\r\nToday morning after breakfast checkout from the hotel and drive to Chandigarh. Reach Chandigarh and check in to the hotel. Dinner and overnight stay.\";i:7;s:238:\"MEALS:  Breakfast only\r\nToday have breakfast and check out from the hotel. Visit Rose Garden, Rock Garden &amp; Sukhna Lake and drive to Delhi. Reach Delhi and you will dropped at Delhi railway station or airport for your further journey.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:7:{i:1;s:210:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Dinner only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On arrival Delhi Airport you will meet with our assisted and drive for Shimla, on arrival check in to the hotel, Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel…&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:340:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Breakfast &amp; Dinner only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today morning after breakfast proceed towards famous ski Point - KUFRI (Including Kufri Fun Park).  Rest of the evening free to explore THE MALL ROAD, RIDGE, SCANDAL POINT, LAKKAR BAZAAR, CHRIST CHURCH AND LOWER BAZAAR BY OWN. Dinner &amp; Overnight stay at the hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:3;s:342:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS:  Breakfast &amp; Dinner&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out from the hotel and drive to Shimla enrooted visit Kullu, valley, Kullu shawl industry, Vaishno Devi Temple. Have photographs at Pandoh Dam &amp; Sundernaggar Lake. Evening reach Shimla and check into the hotel. Dinner &amp; overnight stay at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:4;s:526:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS:   Breakfast &amp; Dinner only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today morning after breakfast  proceed to half day city tour of Manali which includes- HADIMBA DEVI TEMPLE (Built in 1553 A.D , is Dedicated to Himachal\'s Most Significant Deity Hadimba Mata) VASHISTH HOT SPRINGS (Dedicated to Vashisth Muni &amp; Renowned for its hot Curable water),CLUB HOUSE. Later free to explore the local market (MALL ROAD &amp; IBEX MARKET) of Manali, TIBETAN MONASTERY AND VAN VIHAR by own. Dinner &amp; overnight stay at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:5;s:413:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS: Breakfast &amp; Dinner only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today have excursion trip to ROHTANG PASS up to snow line (up to Snow line refers to the barrier placed by the government to avoid risks during Heavy snowfall).  Tour to Rohtang covers some of the most attractive spots, panorama activities and spectacular sight of glaciers. IN EVENING RETURN TO MANALI. Dinner &amp; overnight stay at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:6;s:217:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS:  Breakfast &amp; Dinner&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today morning after breakfast checkout from the hotel and drive to Chandigarh. Reach Chandigarh and check in to the hotel. Dinner and overnight stay.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:7;s:274:\"&lt;p&gt;MEALS:  Breakfast only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today have breakfast and check out from the hotel. Visit Rose Garden, Rock Garden &amp; Sukhna Lake and drive to Delhi. Reach Delhi and you will dropped at Delhi railway station or airport for your further journey.&lt;/p&gt;\";}}s:4:\"cost\";a:6:{s:14:\"includes_title\";s:22:\"The Trip Cost Includes\";s:13:\"cost_includes\";s:710:\"Pick-up or Drop-off service from and to Airport(in our own vehicle)\r\n    Transportation to and from!!\r\n    Food all along the trip(Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner and a cup of coffee or tea) and accommodations during the trip in hotels with family environment\r\n    Transportation, food, accommodation and insurance of Guide during the trip \r\n    Down jacket, all-season sleeping bag, duffel bag and trekking map(in case if you don’t have your own. Down jacket, sleeping bag and duffel bag must be returned after completion of the trip)\r\n    First Aid Medical Kit(Your guide will carry the Medical Kit but we also advise to bring yourself for your own use, as far as possible)\r\nAll the required permits and paperwork\";s:17:\"cost_includes_val\";s:845:\"&lt;li&gt;Pick-up or Drop-off service from and to Airport(in our own vehicle)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;    Transportation to and from!!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;    Food all along the trip(Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner and a cup of coffee or tea) and accommodations during the trip in hotels with family environment&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;    Transportation, food, accommodation and insurance of Guide during the trip &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;    Down jacket, all-season sleeping bag, duffel bag and trekking map(in case if you don’t have your own. Down jacket, sleeping bag and duffel bag must be returned after completion of the trip)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;    First Aid Medical Kit(Your guide will carry the Medical Kit but we also advise to bring yourself for your own use, as far as possible)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All the required permits and paperwork&lt;/li&gt;\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:22:\"The Trip Cost Excludes\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:424:\"International Airfare\r\n    Visa Charges\r\n    Hotel Expenses(In Kathmandu, some packages do include hotel expenses)\r\n    Your travel and medical insurance \r\n    Personal Expenses such as shopping, bar bills, hot shower, telephone, laundry, titbits etc\r\n    Food and accommodations in Kathmandu  \r\n    Services not mentioned or not promised by the agent/agency\r\n    Emergency expenses such as expenses on chartered helicopter.\";s:17:\"cost_excludes_val\";s:582:\"&lt;li&gt;    International Airfare&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;    Visa Charges&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;    Hotel Expenses(In Kathmandu, some packages 