(678, 268, 'wp_travel_engine_setting', 'a:10:{s:15:\"trip_prev_price\";s:5:\"24999\";s:4:\"sale\";s:1:\"1\";s:10:\"trip_price\";s:5:\"19999\";s:13:\"trip_duration\";s:2:\"10\";s:20:\"trip_duration_nights\";s:1:\"9\";s:11:\"tab_content\";a:2:{s:10:\"1_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"map_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";}s:9:\"itinerary\";a:3:{s:15:\"itinerary_title\";a:10:{i:1;s:30:\"Delhi-Shimla (370 km, 9-10 hr)\";i:2;s:31:\"Shimla- Kufri-Local Sightseeing\";i:3;s:43:\"Shimla-Kullu valley-Manali (256 kms/8-9 hr)\";i:4;s:52:\"Manali- Rohtang Pass (up to snow line)-Solang Valley\";i:5;s:25:\"Manali- Local Sightseeing\";i:6;s:36:\"Manali-Dharamshala (280 Kms/8-9 hrs)\";i:7;s:50:\"Dharamshala-sightseeing-Dalhousie (127 km 4-5 hrs)\";i:8;s:28:\"Dalhousie-Khajjiar-Dalhousie\";i:9;s:42:\"Dalhousie-Chandigarh [330 kmtrs 9 -10 hrs]\";i:10;s:53:\"Chandigah sightseeing-Delhi drop [250 kmtrs 5 -6 hrs]\";}s:17:\"itinerary_content\";a:10:{i:1;s:256:\"On arrival at DELHI AIRPORT/RAILWAY STATION you will meet and greet with our representative and start your journey for Shimla. On the way you can visit beautiful spot like Timber Trail. On arrival at Shimla check in the hotel, dinner and rest in the hotel.\";i:2;s:586:\"After breakfast proceed for Kufri sightseeing “KUFRI” INDIA\'S One of the Best Holiday Paradise famous for its Himalayan park, pony and yak ride one can see wide endless Himalayan panorama from Kufri, also take a romantic view of Thick Deodar and pine forest. After this back to Shimla, transfer to lift, visit THEMALL ROAD. AT MALL ROAD YOU CAN VISIT- THE RIDGE, SCANDAL POINT, THE WORLD FAMOUS INTERNATIONAL GAIETY THEATER, TOWN HALL, LAKKAR BAZAAR, CHRIST CHURCH, KALI BARI TEMPLE, and shopping for family, friends and loved one, back to hotel, dinner and rest overnight at hotel.\";i:3;s:272:\"After breakfast check out from the hotel and leave for MANALI, ENROOTED VISIT  SUNDER LAKE, PANDOH DAM, HANOGI MATA TEMPLE, KULLU VALLEY, KULLU SHAWL INDUSTRY, VAISHNO MATA TEMPLE, in evening reached at Manali check in to the hotel, Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.\";i:4;s:511:\"This day after breakfast excursion to ROHTANG PASS (UP TO SNOW LINE), situated at an altitude of 3979 mtrs above sea level and 51 kms outside Manali is the mighty Rohtang Pass – the gateway to Lahoul-Spiti Valley. It affords a wide panoramic view of the mountains. Here one sees the majesty of the mountains at its height and splendor. At the top of the pass the air seems to glitter against the snow as you look down over herringboned ridges into the Lahaul valley. Dinner at hotel over night stay in Manali.\";i:5;s:646:\"After breakfast visit to VASHISTH BATH (Vashisth Springs is situated at Vashisth village, just 3 Km from Manali. Sulphur springs gush forth from the mountains here and these springs have medicinal properties. A bath complex with a restaurant caters to the tourists.)Temples dedicated to Sage Vashisth and Lord Rama are located nearby), HADIMBA TEMPLE (Hadimba Temple is one of the most important temples in the region. This four story wooden temple is located in the middle of a forest called the Dhungiri). CLUB HOUSE. TIBETAN MONASTERY, VAN VIHAR, AND THE MALL ROAD Evening free for shopping on The Mall Road. Dinner and Overnight stay at Hotel\";i:6;s:210:\"This dayafter breakfast check out hotel and depart for DHARAMSHALA. On the way visit BABA BAIJ NATH TEMPLE, PALAMPUR TEA ESTATE AND CHAMUNDA TEMPLE. On arrival check in hotel dinner and overnight stay at hotel.\";i:7;s:238:\"After breakfast check out hotel visit His Holiness DALALI LAMA TEMPLE, BHAGSU NATH TEMPLE, MECLOEDGANJ, ST.JOHN CHURCH AND LOCAL MARKET. After this depart for Dalhousie. On arrival check in hotel. Dinner at hotel. Overnight stay at Hotel.\";i:8;s:205:\"After breakfast Depart for KHAJJIAR. VISIT SUBHASH BOLI, PANCHPULA, KALATOP, KHAJJIAR (India`s Mini Switzerland, a beautiful glade with the forest at its fringes.) Dinner at hotel. Overnight stay at Hotel.\";i:9;s:130:\"After breakfast check out hotel and depart for CHANDIGARH. In Chandigarh check in hotel. Rest, dinner and overnight stay in hotel.\";i:10;s:215:\"After breakfast check out hotel. Local sightseeing of Chandigarh-ROCKGARDEN, SUKHNA LAKE AND ROSE GARDEN. After sightseeing depart for Delhi. Drop at Delhi Airport/Railway Station. End of your tour and our services.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:10:{i:1;s:275:\"&lt;p&gt;On arrival at DELHI AIRPORT/RAILWAY STATION you will meet and greet with our representative and start your journey for Shimla. On the way you can visit beautiful spot like Timber Trail. On arrival at Shimla check in the hotel, dinner and rest in the hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:606:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast proceed for Kufri sightseeing “KUFRI” INDIA\'S One of the Best Holiday Paradise famous for its Himalayan park, pony and yak ride one can see wide endless Himalayan panorama from Kufri, also take a romantic view of Thick Deodar and pine forest. After this back to Shimla, transfer to lift, visit THEMALL ROAD. AT MALL ROAD YOU CAN VISIT- THE RIDGE, SCANDAL POINT, THE WORLD FAMOUS INTERNATIONAL GAIETY THEATER, TOWN HALL, LAKKAR BAZAAR, CHRIST CHURCH, KALI BARI TEMPLE, and shopping for family, friends and loved one, back to hotel, dinner and rest overnight at hotel. &lt;/p&gt;\";i:3;s:291:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out from the hotel and leave for MANALI, ENROOTED VISIT  SUNDER LAKE, PANDOH DAM, HANOGI MATA TEMPLE, KULLU VALLEY, KULLU SHAWL INDUSTRY, VAISHNO MATA TEMPLE, in evening reached at Manali check in to the hotel, Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:4;s:530:\"&lt;p&gt;This day after breakfast excursion to ROHTANG PASS (UP TO SNOW LINE), situated at an altitude of 3979 mtrs above sea level and 51 kms outside Manali is the mighty Rohtang Pass – the gateway to Lahoul-Spiti Valley. It affords a wide panoramic view of the mountains. Here one sees the majesty of the mountains at its height and splendor. At the top of the pass the air seems to glitter against the snow as you look down over herringboned ridges into the Lahaul valley. Dinner at hotel over night stay in Manali.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:5;s:665:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast visit to VASHISTH BATH (Vashisth Springs is situated at Vashisth village, just 3 Km from Manali. Sulphur springs gush forth from the mountains here and these springs have medicinal properties. A bath complex with a restaurant caters to the tourists.)Temples dedicated to Sage Vashisth and Lord Rama are located nearby), HADIMBA TEMPLE (Hadimba Temple is one of the most important temples in the region. This four story wooden temple is located in the middle of a forest called the Dhungiri). CLUB HOUSE. TIBETAN MONASTERY, VAN VIHAR, AND THE MALL ROAD Evening free for shopping on The Mall Road. Dinner and Overnight stay at Hotel&lt;/p&gt;\";i:6;s:229:\"&lt;p&gt;This dayafter breakfast check out hotel and depart for DHARAMSHALA. On the way visit BABA BAIJ NATH TEMPLE, PALAMPUR TEA ESTATE AND CHAMUNDA TEMPLE. On arrival check in hotel dinner and overnight stay at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:7;s:257:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out hotel visit His Holiness DALALI LAMA TEMPLE, BHAGSU NATH TEMPLE, MECLOEDGANJ, ST.JOHN CHURCH AND LOCAL MARKET. After this depart for Dalhousie. On arrival check in hotel. Dinner at hotel. Overnight stay at Hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:8;s:225:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast Depart for KHAJJIAR. VISIT SUBHASH BOLI, PANCHPULA, KALATOP, KHAJJIAR (India`s Mini Switzerland, a beautiful glade with the forest at its fringes.) Dinner at hotel. Overnight stay at Hotel. &lt;/p&gt;\";i:9;s:149:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out hotel and depart for CHANDIGARH. In Chandigarh check in hotel. Rest, dinner and overnight stay in hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:10;s:234:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out hotel. Local sightseeing of Chandigarh-ROCKGARDEN, SUKHNA LAKE AND ROSE GARDEN. After sightseeing depart for Delhi. Drop at Delhi Airport/Railway Station. End of your tour and our services.&lt;/p&gt;\";}}s:4:\"cost\";a