ad back to Hotel rest and followed by dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.\";i:5;s:33:\"Sangla- Kalpa (23kms / 1-1:30hrs)\";i:6;s:176:\"After your morning breakfast pay a visit to the wonderful apple Gardens and surrounding villages. Head back to Hotel rest and followed by dinner and overnight stay in the hotel\";i:7;s:238:\"After your delicious breakfast drives towards Tabo enroot visit beautiful Nako village which is located at the banks of small lake. On arrival check in to the hotel fresh up and enjoy your delicious dinner and overnight stay at the hotel.\";i:8;s:245:\"Today after your morning breakfast pay a visit to famous Tabo monastery, after your visit heads towards Kaza enroot visit Lalung and Dhankar Gompa. On reaching Kaza check in to the hotel followed by dinner and overnight stay at hotel in leisure.\";i:9;s:545:\"Today after your morning breakfast pays a visit to Amazing Ki Monastery which is located at the distance of 12kms away from Kaza. These centuries old monastery is a labyrinth of rooms and corridors – and at one time also acted as a fort. It houses valuable Thangka and offers a panoramic view of the area. Also visit the small Gompa at Kibber, 9 Kms further ahead. Kibber at 4205 m has the distinction of being the highest permanently inhabited village of the region back to the hotel followed by dinner and overnight stay at hotel in leisure.\";i:10;s:302:\"Today after your breakfast check out from the hotel and drive towards Manali crossing Losar village and cross two famous and wonderful passes Kunzum and Rohtang pass. On arrival to Manali after long journey check in to the hotel fresh up and enjoy your delicious dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.\";i:11;s:412:\"After Breakfast proceed for local sightseeing of Manali which includes famous and oldest Hadimba Devi temple, Manu Temple and Natural Vashisth Hot water spring [known for medicinal use], Afternoon half day tour visiting Nagger Heritage village to visit Nagger Castle, Roerich Art Gallery, Tripura Sundri Temple and Shiva Temple. Head back towards Manali .Followed by delicious Dinner and overnight stay at Hotel.\";i:12;s:220:\"After breakfast check out hotel from Manali, proceed to Chandigarh. Reach Chandigarh and you will drop at Chandigarh airport for your further journey. End of your tour and our services. Hope to serve you again in future.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:12:{i:1;s:357:\"&lt;p&gt;On arrival to respected station you will be greet by our driver. Start your journey towards Shimla. On reaching Shimla drop to respected Hotel check in to the Hotel fresh up. In the evening make a visit at famous Shimla Mall .Back to Hotel followed by delicious dinner and overnight stay in the hotel&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:345:\"&lt;p&gt;After your morning delicious breakfast drives towards Sarahan enroot visit Kufri, sun temple at Nirath and Rampur. On arrival check in to the hotel fresh up. In the evening visit Bhimakali temple which is one of the 51 shaktipeeths of the Hindu religion. Drive back to hotel followed by dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:3;s:342:\"&lt;p&gt;Today after your morning breakfast drive towards Sangla valley. On arrival check in to the hotel visit remote villages of Rackcham and enjoy the natural beauty of the village and the people of the village. Head back to Hotel rest and followed by dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:4;s:250:\"&lt;p&gt;Today after your morning breakfast day is free for excursion to Chitkul, the last village on Indo-Chinese border. Head back to Hotel rest and followed by dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:5;s:53:\"&lt;p&gt; Sangla- Kalpa (23kms / 1-1:30hrs)&lt;/p&gt;\";i:6;s:233:\"&lt;p&gt;After your morning breakfast pay a visit to the wonderful apple Gardens and surrounding villages. Head back to Hotel rest and followed by dinner an