llowed by delicious Dinner and overnight stay at Hotel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:12;s:239:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out hotel from Manali, proceed to Chandigarh. Reach Chandigarh and you will drop at Chandigarh airport for your further journey. End of your tour and our services. Hope to serve you again in future.&lt;/p&gt;\";}}s:4:\"cost\";a:6:{s:14:\"includes_title\";s:52:\"Non Ac Cab for Kinnaur Spiti Tour from ex Chandigarh\";s:13:\"cost_includes\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"cost_includes_val\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:37:\"Monuments entry fees and camera fees.\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"cost_excludes_val\";s:0:\"\";}s:3:\"faq\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}s:3:\"map\";a:2:{s:9:\"image_url\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"iframe\";s:0:\"\";}}'),
