(1511, 658, 'wp_travel_engine_setting', 'a:9:{s:15:\"trip_prev_price\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"trip_price\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"trip_duration\";s:2:\"13\";s:20:\"trip_duration_nights\";s:2:\"14\";s:11:\"tab_content\";a:2:{s:10:\"1_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"map_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";}s:9:\"itinerary\";a:3:{s:15:\"itinerary_title\";a:14:{i:1;s:38:\"CHANDIGARH TO SHIMLA (140 KMS 3-4 HRS)\";i:2;s:6:\"SHIMLA\";i:3;s:35:\"SHIMLA TO SARAHAN (163 KMS 4-5 HRS)\";i:4;s:34:\"SARAHAN TO SANGLA (97 KMS 2-3 HRS)\";i:5;s:32:\"SANGLA TO KALPA (40 KMS 1-2 HRS)\";i:6;s:32:\"SANGLA TO KALPA (40 KMS 1-2 HRS)\";i:7;s:27:\"TABO TO KAZA( 50 KMS 1 HRS)\";i:8;s:4:\"KAZA\";i:9;s:32:\"KAZA TO MANALI (203 KMS 4-5 HRS)\";i:10;s:6:\"MANALI\";i:11;s:38:\"MANALI TO DHARAMSALA (235 KMS 6-7 HRS)\";i:12;s:10:\"DHARAMSALA\";i:13;s:40:\"DHARAMSALA TO AMRITSAR (210 KMS 4-5 HRS)\";i:14;s:35:\"AMRITSAR TO DELHI (452 KMS(8-9 HRS)\";}s:17:\"itinerary_content\";a:14:{i:1;s:184:\"On Arrival in Chandigarh Airport/ Railway Station meet our representative and transfer by road from Chandigarh to Shimla. On Arrival check in at hotel. Overnight stay at Sarahan Hotel.\";i:2;s:664:\"This Day after breakfast check out from the hotel proceed for in and around sightseeing of SHIMLA, visit KUFRI, India\'s one of the best holiday paradise Kufri in Shimla is beautifully tucked on an altitude of 2,622 meter. The place is a tourist hotspot for its awesome scenic and sports activities. Evening free to stroll in the famous shopping place of Shimla town – &quot;THE MALL &amp; THE RIDGE&quot; This large open space in the heart of town presents excellent views of the mountain ranges. Shimla\'s landmarks - the neo- gothic structure of Christ Church and the neo - Tudor library building - are worth seeing.\r\nDinner and overnight stay in the hotel.....\";i:3;s:346:\"Travel by surface from Shimla, the gateway to Kinnaur Enroute crossing the famous hill resorts of Kufri &amp; Narkanda. Enroute also visit Rampur and view Padam Palace. Continue drive along the Satluj River and from Jeori clime up to Sarahan. On arrival check in at hotel. Evening visit the famous Bhimakali Temple at Sarahan. Overnight at hotel.\";i:4;s:83:\"Visit remote village of Rackham and Chitkul Village .over night stay in camp/hotel.\";i:5;s:333:\"After breakfast travel to Sangla which has earned distinction of one of the most beautiful valleys in Himachal. At Sangla visit Kamru village and make a small walk to visit kamru Fort which has a temple dedicated to Kamaksha Devi. Later check in at camp. Rest of day is free to relax and enjoy the pristine beauty .Overnight at camp.\";i:6;s:51:\"Visit Nako village. Overnight in the hotel at Tabo.\";i:7;s:108:\"Today visit to Tabo monastery, Lalung and Dhankar Gompa , Later then drive to kaza. Overnight in kaza hotel.\";i:8;s:164:\"Today visit the Ki monastery and Kibber (4205) village. In the afternoon travel to Tashigong village to see the LA darcha Fair grounds and the Chao Kang Nilda peak.\";i:9;s:90:\"Driving over Kunzam Pass 4558 m and Rohtang Pass 3980m. Arrive evening in Manali at hotel.\";i:10;s:632:\"After breakfast visit to Vashisth Bath (Vashisth Springs is situated at Vashisth village, just 3 Km from Manali. Sulfur springs gush forth from the mountains here and these springs have medicinal properties. A bath complex with a restaurant caters to the tourists.)Temples dedicated to Sage Vashisth and Lord Rama are located nearby), Hadimba Temple (Hadimba Temple is one of the most important temples in the region. This four story wooden temple is located in the middle of a forest called the Dhungiri). Tibetan Monastery, Club House. Evening free for shopping on The Mall Road and Ibex market. Dinner and Overnight stay at Hotel\";i:11;s:322:\"After breakfast check out from hotel and depart for Dharamshala. Enroute cover sightseeing of Kullu Valley, Rafting Point, Kullu shawl industry cum showroom &amp; Vaishno Devi Temple. Also cover Tea Gardens &amp; Baijnath Temple inking Valley. Evening arrive at Dharamshala. Check into the hotel dinner and overnight stay.\";i:12;s:101:\"This morning visit to Dalai Lama Temple in Macleodganj, Norbulinka Institute, Bhagsunag and Dal lake.\";i:13;s:180:\"Early in morning drive to Amritsar on arrival check in to hotel after fresh up visit Golden Temple, Jillian Walla Bagh and Bagha Border ceremony dinner and overnight stay at hotel.\";i:14;s:154:\"Next day check out the hotel and drive for Delhi .In evening reached Delhi and drop at Delhi Airport/Railway Station. End of our service and your journey.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:14:{i:1;s:222:\"&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On Arrival in Chandigarh Airport/ Railway Station meet our representative and transfer by road from Chandigarh to Shimla. On Arrival check in at hotel. Overnight stay at Sarahan Hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:719:\"&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This Day after breakfast check out from the hotel proceed for in and around sightseeing of SHIMLA, visit KUFRI, India\'s one of the best holiday paradise Kufri in Shimla is beautifully tucked on an altitude of 2,622 meter. The place is a tourist hotspot for its awesome scenic and sports activities. Evening free to stroll in the famous shopping place of Shimla town – &quot;THE MALL &amp; THE RIDGE&quot; This large open space in the heart of town presents excellent views of the mountain ranges. Shimla\'s landmarks - the neo- gothic structure of Christ Church and the neo - Tudor library building - are worth seeing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel.....&lt;/p&gt;\";i:3;s:403:\"&lt;p&gt;Travel by surface from Shimla, the gateway to Kinnaur Enroute crossing the famous hill resorts of Kufri &amp; Narkanda. Enroute also visit Rampur and view Padam Palace. Continue drive along the Satluj River and from Jeori clime up to Sarahan. On arrival check in at hotel. Evening visit the famous Bhimakali Temple at Sarahan. Overnight at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:4;s:140:\"&lt;p&gt;Visit remote village of Rackham and Chitkul Village .over night stay in camp/hotel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:5;s:390:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast travel to Sangla which has earned distinction of one of the most beautiful valleys in Himachal. At Sangla visit Kamru village and make a small walk to visit kamru Fort which has a temple dedicated to Kamaksha Devi. Later check in at camp. Rest of day is free to relax and enjoy the pristine beauty .Overnight at camp.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:6;s:128:\"&lt;p&gt; Visit Nako village. Overnight in the hotel at Tabo.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:7;s:146:\"&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today visit to Tabo monastery, Lalung and Dhankar Gompa , Later then drive to kaza. Overnight in kaza hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:8;s:202:\"&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today visit the Ki monastery and Kibber (4205) village. In the afternoon travel to Tashigong village to see the LA darcha Fair grounds and the Chao Kang Nilda peak.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:9;s:128:\"&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Driving over Kunzam Pass 4558 m and Rohtang Pass 3980m. Arrive evening in Manali at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:10;s:689:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast visit to Vashisth Bath (Vashisth Springs is situated at Vashisth village, just 3 Km from Manali. Sulfur springs gush forth from the mountains here and these springs have medicinal properties. A bath complex with a restaurant caters to the tourists.)Temples dedicated to Sage Vashisth and Lord Rama are located nearby), Hadimba Temple (Hadimba Temple is one of the most important temples in the region. This four story wooden temple is located in the middle of a forest called the Dhungiri). Tibetan Monastery, Club House. Evening free for shopping on The Mall Road and Ibex market. Dinner and Overnight stay at Hotel&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:11;s:341:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast check out from hotel and depart for Dharamshala. Enroute cover sightseeing of Kullu Valley, Rafting Point, Kullu shawl industry cum showroom &amp; Vaishno Devi Temple. Also cover Tea Gardens &amp; Baijnath Temple inking Valley. Evening arrive at Dharamshala. Check into the hotel dinner and overnight stay.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:12;s:158:\"&lt;p&gt;This morning visit to Dalai Lama Temple in Macleodganj, Norbulinka Institute, Bhagsunag and Dal lake.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:13;s:199:\"&lt;p&gt;Early in morning drive to Amritsar on arrival check in to hotel after fresh up visit Golden Temple, Jillian Walla Bagh and Bagha Border ceremony dinner and overnight stay at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:14;s:192:\"&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Next day check out the hotel and drive for Delhi .In evening reached Delhi and drop at Delhi Airport/Railway Station. End of our service and your journey.&lt;/p&gt;\";}}s:4:\"cost\";a:6:{s:14:\"includes_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"cost_includes\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"cost_includes_val\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"cost_excludes_val\";s:0:\"\";}s:3:\"faq\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}s:3:\"map\";a:2:{s:9:\"image_url\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"iframe\";s:0:\"\";}}'),
