 the early morning of the penultimate day, an excursion is scheduled to Pangong Lake, a 135 km drive from Leh. The Pangong Lake is 140km long and 3-5km in width – more than half of which lies in Tibetan territory. As you return back Leh by evening, you can use the remaining time exploring local markets, looking for a decent bargain. Overnight stay is again at the hotel. &lt;/p&gt;\";i:8;s:325:\"&lt;p&gt;Morning check out from hotel &amp; drive towards Kargil which is 230 kilometers from Leh town. Enroute you can cover Magnetic Hill, Pathar Sahib Gurudwara &amp; Confluence of Indus &amp; Zanskar river. By the evening, arrive Kargil and check in at the hotel in Kargil.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:9;s:153:\"&lt;p&gt;Morning check out from hotel &amp; depart for Srinagar. Evening arrive at Srinagar. Drop at Srinagar Airport for your further journey.&lt;/p&gt;\";}}s:4:\"cost\";a:6:{s:14:\"includes_title\";s:15:\"Price Includes:\";s:13:\"cost_includes\";s:352:\"Hotel Accommodation for 08 nights/09 days.\r\n  Welcome Drink On arrival (non alcohol like Tea,Coffee,Juice )\r\n  M.A.P. Plan:- 05 Breakfast + 05 Dinner [ Veg Food only)\r\n Internal sightseeing in Leh will be done by Scorpio/Xylo/innova\r\n Inclusive Of All the applicable taxes (Hotel Luxury Tax, Hotel Service tax, Fuel Charges, Parking, Driver allowance).\";s:17:\"cost_includes_val\";s:450:\"&lt;li&gt; Hotel Accommodation for 08 nights/09 days.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;  Welcome Drink On arrival (non alcohol like Tea,Coffee,Juice )&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;  M.A.P. Plan:- 05 Breakfast + 05 Dinner [ Veg Food only)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Internal sightseeing in Leh will be done by Scorpio/Xylo/innova&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Inclusive Of All the applicable taxes (Hotel Luxury Tax, Hotel Service tax, Fuel Charges, Parking, Driver allowance).&lt;/li&gt;\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:22:\"Price doesn\'t Include:\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:1353:\"Any type of Local Transportation excluding the provided sightseein