ymoon cake (once during the stay) &lt;/li&gt;\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:22:\"Price doesn\'t Include:\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"cost_excludes_val\";s:0:\"\";}s:3:\"faq\";a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:3:\"FAQ\";s:9:\"faq_title\";a:1:{i:1;s:18:\"Cancelation policy\";}s:11:\"faq_content\";a:1:{i:1;s:405:\"For cancellations done prior to 45 days or more of departure, 30%\r\nCancellation fees would apply.\r\nFor cancellations done between 31 to 44 days of departure, 50%\r\nCancellation fees would apply.\r\nFor cancellations done between 11 to 30 days of departure, 75%\r\nCancellation fees would apply.\r\nFor cancellations done within 10 days of departure, 100% cancellation\r\nFees would apply. No refunds would be made.\";}}s:3:\"map\";a:2:{s:9:\"image_url\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"iframe\";s:0:\"\";}}'),
