(1824, 712, 'wp_travel_engine_setting', 'a:9:{s:15:\"trip_prev_price\";s:5:\"70000\";s:10:\"trip_price\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"trip_duration\";s:2:\"21\";s:20:\"trip_duration_nights\";s:2:\"20\";s:11:\"tab_content\";a:2:{s:10:\"1_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"map_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";}s:9:\"itinerary\";a:3:{s:15:\"itinerary_title\";a:21:{i:1;s:13:\"Arrival Delhi\";i:2;s:56:\"Delhi – Mandawa (Shekhawati) ( appr. 280 km, 6 hours )\";i:3;s:45:\"Mandawa – Bikaner( appr. 200 km , 4 hours )\";i:4;s:44:\"Bikaner – Khuri ( appr. 360 km , 7 hours )\";i:5;s:44:\"Khuri – jaisalmer( appr. 50 km , 1 hours )\";i:6;s:48:\"Jaisalmer – Jodhpur ( appr. 300 km , 6 hours )\";i:7;s:45:\"Jodhpur -  Mt. Abu ( appr. 250 km , 5 hours )\";i:8;s:48:\"Mt. Abu – Ranakpur ( appr. 190 km , 4 hours  )\";i:9;s:66:\"Ranakpur – Udaipur ( via Kumbalgarh) ( appr. 140 km , 3 hours  )\";i:10;s:7:\"Udaipur\";i:11;s:49:\"Udaipur – Chitorgarh ( appr. 120 km , 2 hours )\";i:12;s:47:\"Chitorgarh – Bundi ( appr. 150 km , 3 hours )\";i:13;s:46:\"Bundi – Pushkar   ( appr. 280 km , 6 hours )\";i:14;s:44:\"Pushkar -  Jaipur ( appr. 150 km , 3 hours )\";i:15;s:6:\"Jaipur\";i:16;s:50:\"Jaipur – Ranthambhore ( appr. 200 km , 4 hours )\";i:17;s:52:\"Ranthambhore -  Bharatpur ( appr. 240 km , 5 hours )\";i:18;s:46:\"Bharatpur -  Agra (appr.  60 km , 1:30 hours )\";i:19;s:42:\"Agra - Delhi ( appr. 220 km , 4:30 hours )\";i:20;s:11:\"Delhi Local\";i:21;s:5:\"Delhi\";}s:17:\"itinerary_content\";a:21:{i:1;s:128:\"Arrive in  Delhi Airport/Railway station you will be met, assisted and derive to Delhi hotel and overnight stay in Delhi hotels.\";i:2;s:215:\"After breakfast drive to Mandawa, on the way you will see countryside, traditional villages; colourful, beautiful painted have lies. Mandawa and Jhunjhunu are the major towns of Shikawati, overnight stay in Mandawa.\";i:3;s:167:\"After breakfast drive to Bikaner, sightseeing of Bikaner like Rat Temple, Junagarh Fort, Camel Breeding Farm, evening walk around of bazaar, overnight stay in Bikaner.\";i:4;s:259:\"After the breakfast drive to Khuri, this is the part of desert and it is the name of traditional village. You can do overnight camel safari there and you can sleep under the open sky in the desert or  in hotel(depends on your wish), overnight stay in  desert.\";i:5;s:221:\"After breakfast drive to jaisalmer, sightseeing of jaisalmer like jaisalmer Fort, Jain Temple, Patwan – Ki – Haveli, Salim – Singh – Ki – Haveli, Gadhi Sagar and sunset in Bada Bagh, overnight stay in jaisalmer.\";i:6;s:169:\"After breakfast move to Jodhpur, sightseeing of Jodhpur like Mahrangarh Fort, Jaswant Thada, Evening walk around in clock tower, Spicy Bazaar, overnight stay in Jodhpur.\";i:7;s:209:\"After breakfast drive to Mt. Abu, it is a big tourist destination, sightseeing of Mt. Abu like Dilwara Jain Temple, Naki Lake here sunset and honey moon points are the famous points, overnight stay in Mt. Abu.\";i:8;s:183:\"After breakfast drive to ranakpur ,sightseeing of Ranakpur like chaumukha temple ( Jain Temple ) . It is the main Temple consist 1444 pillars and 29 halls. Overnight stay in Ranakpur.\";i:9;s:192:\"After breakfast drive to Kumbalgarh fort. Kumbalgarh fort is the most important fort in the mewar region after Chittorgarh, built in 15th century by Maharana Kumbha, overnight stay in Udaipur.\";i:10;s:178:\"Sightseeing of Udaipur like City Palace, Jagdish Temple, Boating in Lake Pichola, Bagor Ki Haveli, Saheliyon Ki Bari, Mansoon Palace, walk around in bazaar, overnight in Udaipur.\";i:11;s:204:\"After breakfast Drive to Chittorgah sightseeing of Chittorgarh Fort (inside Ranakumbha Palace, Fateh Parakash Palace, Tower of Victory, Padamni Palace, Sammideshwar Temple), overnight stay in Chittorgarh.\";i:12;s:158:\"After breakfast move for Bundi, sightseeing of Bundi like evening sightseeing of Tarh Garh Fort and Bundi Palace, walk around bazaar, overnight stay in Bundi.\";i:13;s:144:\"After breakfast drive to Pushkar, in evening walkaround of Pushkar City and Lake. This is called Land of Lord Bhrama, overnight stay in Pushkar.\";i:14;s:137:\"After breakfast drive to Jaipur, sightseeing of Jaipur like Birla Temple, Albert Hall, walk around in Pink City, overnight stay in Jaipur\";i:15;s:193:\"After breakfast sightseeing of Jal Mahal ( Water Palace ), Amber Palace, Hawa Mahal (Wind Palace) , City Palace , Gettore , Janter Manter , walk around the pink city , overnight stay in Jaipur.\";i:16;s:138:\"After breakfast drive to Ranthambhore. Tiger safari at forest in evening time ( or next day morning time ) ,overnight stay in Ranthambhore\";i:17;s:139:\"After breakfast drive to Bharatpur ( visit step well on the way ) in evening, sightseeing of Bird Century Park, overnight stay in Bharatpur\";i:18;s:117:\"Drive to Agra, sightseeing of Fatehpur Sikri on the way. In evening time sunset at Taj Mahal, overnight stay in Agra.\";i:19;s:121:\"After breakfast sightseeing of Red Fort and Sikandra and then drive for Delhi, lunch on the way, overnight stay in Delhi.\";i:20;s:316:\"After breakfast sightseeing of Old Delhi like Red Fort, Jama Masjid, Chandni Chowk Bazaar, Raj Ghat, Akshardham Temple, Lunch in afternoon sightseeing of New Delhi like Humayun\'s Tomb, India Gate, Parliament House, President House, Lotus Temple , Qutub Minar, Laxmi Narayan Temple. Dinner and overnight stay in Delhi\";i:21;s:61:\"Departure to Airport to connecting flight back to your place.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:21:{i:1;s:147:\"&lt;p&gt;Arrive in  Delhi Airport/Railway station you will be met, assisted and derive to Delhi hotel and overnight stay in Delhi hotels.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:234:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to Mandawa, on the way you will see countryside, traditional villages; colourful, beautiful painted have lies. Mandawa and Jhunjhunu are the major towns of Shikawati, overnight stay in Mandawa.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:3;s:186:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to Bikaner, sightseeing of Bikaner like Rat Temple, Junagarh Fort, Camel Breeding Farm, evening walk around of bazaar, overnight stay in Bikaner.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:4;s:297:\"&lt;p&gt;After the breakfast drive to Khuri, this is the part of desert and it is the name of traditional village. You can do overnight camel safari there and you can sleep under the open sky in the desert or  in hotel(depends on your wish), overnight stay in  desert.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:5;s:259:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to jaisalmer, sightseeing of jaisalmer like jaisalmer Fort, Jain Temple, Patwan – Ki – Haveli, Salim – Singh – Ki – Haveli, Gadhi Sagar and sunset in Bada Bagh, overnight stay in jaisalmer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:6;s:188:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast move to Jodhpur, sightseeing of Jodhpur like Mahrangarh Fort, Jaswant Thada, Evening walk around in clock tower, Spicy Bazaar, overnight stay in Jodhpur.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:7;s:247:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to Mt. Abu, it is a big tourist destination, sightseeing of Mt. Abu like Dilwara Jain Temple, Naki Lake here sunset and honey moon points are the famous points, overnight stay in Mt. Abu.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:8;s:221:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to ranakpur ,sightseeing of Ranakpur like chaumukha temple ( Jain Temple ) . It is the main Temple consist 1444 pillars and 29 halls. Overnight stay in Ranakpur.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:9;s:230:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to Kumbalgarh fort. Kumbalgarh fort is the most important fort in the mewar region after Chittorgarh, built in 15th century by Maharana Kumbha, overnight stay in Udaipur.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:10;s:197:\"&lt;p&gt;Sightseeing of Udaipur like City Palace, Jagdish Temple, Boating in Lake Pichola, Bagor Ki Haveli, Saheliyon Ki Bari, Mansoon Palace, walk around in bazaar, overnight in Udaipur.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:11;s:242:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast Drive to Chittorgah sightseeing of Chittorgarh Fort (inside Ranakumbha Palace, Fateh Parakash Palace, Tower of Victory, Padamni Palace, Sammideshwar Temple), overnight stay in Chittorgarh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:12;s:177:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast move for Bundi, sightseeing of Bundi like evening sightseeing of Tarh Garh Fort and Bundi Palace, walk around bazaar, overnight stay in Bundi.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:13;s:163:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to Pushkar, in evening walkaround of Pushkar City and Lake. This is called Land of Lord Bhrama, overnight stay in Pushkar.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:14;s:156:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to Jaipur, sightseeing of Jaipur like Birla Temple, Albert Hall, walk around in Pink City, overnight stay in Jaipur&lt;/p&gt;\";i:15;s:231:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast sightseeing of Jal Mahal ( Water Palace ), Amber Palace, Hawa Mahal (Wind Palace) , City Palace , Gettore , Janter Manter , walk around the pink city , overnight stay in Jaipur.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:16;s:176:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to Ranthambhore. Tiger safari at forest in evening time ( or next day morning time ) ,overnight stay in Ranthambhore&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:17;s:196:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast drive to Bharatpur ( visit step well on the way ) in evening, sightseeing of Bird Century Park, overnight stay in Bharatpur&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:18;s:155:\"&lt;p&gt;Drive to Agra, sightseeing of Fatehpur Sikri on the way. In evening time sunset at Taj Mahal, overnight stay in Agra.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:19;s:178:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast sightseeing of Red Fort and Sikandra and then drive for Delhi, lunch on the way, overnight stay in Delhi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:20;s:373:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast sightseeing of Old Delhi like Red Fort, Jama Masjid, Chandni Chowk Bazaar, Raj Ghat, Akshardham Temple, Lunch in afternoon sightseeing of New Delhi like Humayun\'s Tomb, India Gate, Parliament House, President House, Lotus Temple , Qutub Minar, Laxmi Narayan Temple. Dinner and overnight stay in Delhi&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";i:21;s:80:\"&lt;p&gt;Departure to Airport to connecting flight back to your place.&lt;/p&gt;\";}}s:4:\"cost\";a:6:{s:14:\"includes_title\";s:15:\"Price Includes:\";s:13:\"cost_includes\";s:342:\"Daily Breakfast at Hotel\r\nAirport, Railway Station and Hotel Pickup.\r\nAir Condition Car having, Fuel, Insurance, Toll Taxes\r\nAll State Taxes, Parking and all transport related expense including Driver Services\r\nAccommodation as per our Itinerary hotel on twin sharing basis inclusive of taxes\r\nBelow 5 Yrs Child is Complimentary in the Hotel.\";s:17:\"cost_includes_val\";s:458:\"&lt;li&gt;Daily Breakfast at Hotel&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Airport, Railway Station and Hotel Pickup.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Air Condition Car having, Fuel, Insurance, Toll Taxes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All State Taxes, Parking and all transport related expense including Driver Services&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Accommodation as per our Itinerary hotel on twin sharing basis inclusive of taxes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Below 5 Yrs Child is Complimentary in the Hotel.&lt;/li&gt;\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:22:\"Price doesn\'t Include:\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:198:\"Monuments entry fees and camera fees.\r\nAny which is not mentioned in above package cost.\r\nAny Guide fees/entrainment fees\r\nAny Air and train fare\r\nGovt. Service tax 4.5 % Extra in each tour Packages\";s:17:\"cost_excludes_val\";s:295:\"&lt;li&gt;Monuments entry fees and camera fees.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any which is not mentioned in above package cost.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any Guide fees/entrainment fees&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any Air and train fare&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Govt. Service tax 4.5 % Extra in each tour Packages&lt;/li&gt;\";}s:3:\"faq\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}s:3:\"map\";a:2:{s:9:\"image_url\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"iframe\";s:0:\"\";}}'),
