(1831, 714, 'wp_travel_engine_setting', 'a:9:{s:15:\"trip_prev_price\";s:4:\"9999\";s:10:\"trip_price\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"trip_duration\";s:1:\"8\";s:20:\"trip_duration_nights\";s:1:\"7\";s:11:\"tab_content\";a:2:{s:10:\"1_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"map_wpeditor\";s:0:\"\";}s:9:\"itinerary\";a:3:{s:15:\"itinerary_title\";a:7:{i:1;s:36:\"Welcome To Jaipur”The Pink City”\";i:2;s:35:\"Jaipur To Udaipur (399 Km. 8-9 Hrs)\";i:3;s:19:\"Udaipur Sightseeing\";i:4;s:46:\"Udaipur To Mount Abu (4,003 Ft, 170 Km. 3 Hrs)\";i:5;s:44:\"Mount Abbu To Chittaurgarh (280 Km, 5-6 Hrs)\";i:6;s:47:\"Chittaurgarh To Phushkar-Jaipur (335 Km. 9 Hrs)\";i:7;s:8:\"Drooping\";}s:17:\"itinerary_content\";a:7:{i:1;s:492:\"Arrive Jaipur at your own base. In the morning on arrival at Jaipur Airport/Railway Station/Bus Stand pick up by our company representative and transfer to the respected hotel. After fresh up ready for explore the Pink City. Visit Hawa Mahel, Jantar Mantar, City Palace-in City Palace you can visit various museums and observatory. In the evening visit Chokhi Dhani. Here you can enjoy the art and culture of Rajasthan. You can enjoy traditional and delicious dinner. Overnight Stay at hotel.\";i:2;s:216:\"After breakfast checkout hotel and derive to Udaipur. On the way you can visit Krishna Temple, Nathdwara and Eklingi Temple. Arrive Udaipur in the evening, check in at hotel. Rest, dinner and overnight stay in hotel.\";i:3;s:430:\"This day after having breakfast prepare for full day sightseeing of Udaipur city, founded in 1553 by Maharana Udai Singh.It was voted as a best city in world in 2009.In this city you can visit Lake Palace City Palace,Jag Mandir,Saheliyon Ke Beri and Haldi Ghati.Visit Pichola Lake, an artificial fresh water Lake. Here you can enjoy boating. After the whole day sightseeing back to hotel. Rest, Dinner and overnight stay in hotel.\";i:4;s:448:\"In the morning after breakfast check out hotel and derive to Mount Abbu. It’s a famous hill station in Aravali Range near the border with Gujarat. On arrival check in at hotel.After that visit Dilwara Temple, Arbuda Devi Temple and Guru Shikar, highest point of Mount Abbu. .Mount Abbu is also a location of headquarters of Braham Kumaries.In the evening visit Sunset Point and Nakki Lake. Evening back to hotel diner and overnight stay in hotel.\";i:5;s:328:\"Post breakfast leave for Chittaurgarh. In Chittaurgarh check in at hotel. After\r\n\r\nfresh up visit Chittaurgarh. Main Attractions of Chittaurgarh are-Chittaurgarh Fort, Padmini Palace, Ana Khumba Palace, Vijay Stamb,Priti Stumb,Kalika Mata Temple. After visit the all sightseeing back to hotel, dinner and overnight stay in hotel\";i:6;s:349:\"After having breakfast checks out hotel derive back to Jaipur. Enroute visit Pushkar, famous for its annuel Pushkar Camel Fair. Visit Holy Lake and the only temple of Lord Brahma in the world. You can visit the Rose farm because Phuskar is also famous for rose cultivation. In the evening arrive Jaipur; check in at hotel, dinner and overnight stay.\";i:7;s:306:\"On the last day Proceed for visit Amber Fort. Built by Raja Man Singh 1. It’s in Amer, 11 km. from Jaipur. In this Fort you can enjoy Elephant riding. Visit the Kanak Vrindavan Temple in the valley of flower. After that drop at Jaipur Railway Station/Airport/Bus stand. End of your tour and our services.\";}s:23:\"itinerary_content_inner\";a:7:{i:1;s:511:\"&lt;p&gt;Arrive Jaipur at your own base. In the morning on arrival at Jaipur Airport/Railway Station/Bus Stand pick up by our company representative and transfer to the respected hotel. After fresh up ready for explore the Pink City. Visit Hawa Mahel, Jantar Mantar, City Palace-in City Palace you can visit various museums and observatory. In the evening visit Chokhi Dhani. Here you can enjoy the art and culture of Rajasthan. You can enjoy traditional and delicious dinner. Overnight Stay at hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:2;s:235:\"&lt;p&gt;After breakfast checkout hotel and derive to Udaipur. On the way you can visit Krishna Temple, Nathdwara and Eklingi Temple. Arrive Udaipur in the evening, check in at hotel. Rest, dinner and overnight stay in hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:3;s:449:\"&lt;p&gt;This day after having breakfast prepare for full day sightseeing of Udaipur city, founded in 1553 by Maharana Udai Singh.It was voted as a best city in world in 2009.In this city you can visit Lake Palace City Palace,Jag Mandir,Saheliyon Ke Beri and Haldi Ghati.Visit Pichola Lake, an artificial fresh water Lake. Here you can enjoy boating. After the whole day sightseeing back to hotel. Rest, Dinner and overnight stay in hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:4;s:467:\"&lt;p&gt;In the morning after breakfast check out hotel and derive to Mount Abbu. It’s a famous hill station in Aravali Range near the border with Gujarat. On arrival check in at hotel.After that visit Dilwara Temple, Arbuda Devi Temple and Guru Shikar, highest point of Mount Abbu. .Mount Abbu is also a location of headquarters of Braham Kumaries.In the evening visit Sunset Point and Nakki Lake. Evening back to hotel diner and overnight stay in hotel.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:5;s:381:\"&lt;p&gt;Post breakfast leave for Chittaurgarh. In Chittaurgarh check in at hotel. After&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;fresh up visit Chittaurgarh. Main Attractions of Chittaurgarh are-Chittaurgarh Fort, Padmini Palace, Ana Khumba Palace, Vijay Stamb,Priti Stumb,Kalika Mata Temple. After visit the all sightseeing back to hotel, dinner and overnight stay in hotel&lt;/p&gt;\";i:6;s:368:\"&lt;p&gt;After having breakfast checks out hotel derive back to Jaipur. Enroute visit Pushkar, famous for its annuel Pushkar Camel Fair. Visit Holy Lake and the only temple of Lord Brahma in the world. You can visit the Rose farm because Phuskar is also famous for rose cultivation. In the evening arrive Jaipur; check in at hotel, dinner and overnight stay.&lt;/p&gt;\";i:7;s:325:\"&lt;p&gt;On the last day Proceed for visit Amber Fort. Built by Raja Man Singh 1. It’s in Amer, 11 km. from Jaipur. In this Fort you can enjoy Elephant riding. Visit the Kanak Vrindavan Temple in the valley of flower. After that drop at Jaipur Railway Station/Airport/Bus stand. End of your tour and our services.&lt;/p&gt;\";}}s:4:\"cost\";a:6:{s:14:\"includes_title\";s:15:\"Price Includes:\";s:13:\"cost_includes\";s:259:\"Hotel Accommodation on double sharing basis.\r\nHotel Accommodation for 6 nights on MAP basis(Breakfast &amp; Dinner)\r\nAll the sightseeing with individual AC Cab.\r\nDriver Allowance, Toll Tax and Parking Charges.\r\nAll the applicable Tax except Govt. Service Tax.\";s:17:\"cost_includes_val\";s:356:\"&lt;li&gt;Hotel Accommodation on double sharing basis.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hotel Accommodation for 6 nights on MAP basis(Breakfast &amp; Dinner)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All the sightseeing with individual AC Cab.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Driver Allowance, Toll Tax and Parking Charges.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All the applicable Tax except Govt. Service Tax.&lt;/li&gt;\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:22:\"Price doesn\'t Include:\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:253:\"Tour Exclude:\r\nAny kind of personal expensive such as laundry, Tips, Telephone bill and Camera fee.\r\nEntry fees of any monument.\r\nAny Guide fee and entertainment fees\r\nAny Air fare/train fare/Bus fare\r\nLunch and Unspecified Meals\r\nGovt. Service Tax 4.5%\";s:17:\"cost_excludes_val\";s:388:\"&lt;li&gt;Tour Exclude:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any kind of personal expensive such as laundry, Tips, Telephone bill and Camera fee.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Entry fees of any monument.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any Guide fee and entertainment fees&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any Air fare/train fare/Bus fare&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lunch and Unspecified Meals&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Govt. Service Tax 4.5%&lt;/li&gt;\";}s:3:\"faq\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}s:3:\"map\";a:2:{s:9:\"image_url\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"iframe\";s:0:\"\";}}'),
